{"tid":2188047,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"重啟內地實習  中大浸大港大逼中醫生用健康碼","createTime":"2020-09-04T04:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T10:34:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c8de723bcf806d8d43bafcae62500de659afa231","tid":2188047,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:16:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200904/E2KPNQFZQNBBXPMU2H52XI7YNE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200904%2FE2KPNQFZQNBBXPMU2H52XI7YNE%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cUzY%2BUnkXQH0zW%2FJu7eEK44%3D&h=77735b77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200904%2FE2KPNQFZQNBBXPMU2H52XI7YNE%2F&h=c8503632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200904/E2KPNQFZQNBBXPMU2H52XI7YNE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n重啟內地實習 <br />\n中大浸大港大逼中醫生用健康碼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BGNMYPRA87nAzQx44UE9TO7az84=/2004x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5MISKHDC7ZBRPABJQK5YW7MHVQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBGNMYPRA87nAzQx44UE9TO7az84%3D%2F2004x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5MISKHDC7ZBRPABJQK5YW7MHVQ.jpg&h=c2914e5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中醫學生赴內地實習是院校慣常安排，非法例強制，惟校方拒接受留港實習方案。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「港版健康碼」牽涉私隱風險，引起關注。中大、浸大及港大中醫學院初步訂於9至10月重啟因疫情而暫停的內地實習安排，其中港大及浸大明言學生須使用健康碼。有中大中醫學生指，三校中醫學生使用健康碼在內地有被追蹤風險，擔心會成為首批被迫使用健康碼的犧牲品，加上疫情反覆，要求留港完成實習。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：北上非法定要求<br />\n<br />\n香港中醫學生報考中醫執業。。。<br />\n<br />\n中大中醫北上實習事宜關注。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n存私隱問題 學生憂被追蹤<br />\n<br />\n陳同學指，三校中醫學生非常憂慮使用健康碼會被追蹤，存在私隱問題，而中國官媒新華社曾點名批評中大學生，加上過去亦有實習生受歧視，擔心人身安全風險，同時疫情反覆，亦有健康考慮。他質疑，三大中醫學院未全力保障學生人身和健康安全，只依從中醫藥管理委員會要求，透露已有港大中醫生因此申請延遲畢業，但相信大部份同學雖有不滿，為畢業亦只能「頂硬上」接受安排。<br />\n<br />\n中大中醫學生趙同學（化名）同樣擔心健康碼問題，。。。<br />\n<br />\n中大中醫北上實習事宜關注組表示，。。。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署指，院校可按中。。。"},{"pid":"8ceadb6de15b94f0bb12ab3b9ed903faabe70b40","tid":2188047,"uid":296600,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"要去中国真係避唔到......."},{"pid":"a09ad15c5704504514fdcf2a4b2cc6740ed03b32","tid":2188047,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:34:44.000Z","msg":"中藥有無抗排斥功能？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}